Package: fmi2
Title: Finnish Meteorological Institute open data API R client
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2019-08-13
Authors@R: c(
  person("Joona", "Lehtomaki", email = "jlehtoma@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Ilari", "Scheinin", role = "ctb"))
Description: R client for the Finnish Meteorological Institute (FMI) open data API. This 
  package supersedes the obsolete fmi package. Client can be used to fetch geospatial over
  FMI's WFS (http://en.ilmatieteenlaitos.fi/open-data-manual-accessing-data) and 
  converted into geospatial objects in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
